{"tid":1206041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高官外地子女情況緊急 無聲武器奪命","createTime":"2019-06-12T01:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T07:37:22.000Z","uid":32511,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"65b99225b3c0fb041a33f35ded8a1acffc27d462","tid":1206041,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:12:11.000Z","msg":"要求外地政府警察向高官子女提供人身保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20040218/3863137\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20040218%2F3863137&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e9fce6d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20040218%2F3863137&h=7875a8a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20040218/3863137</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n前任入境處處長梁銘彥的女兒梁詩瀚（二十二歲），在加拿大溫哥華就讀的大學內，遭兇徒以強力的十字弩射殺。梁銘彥在加拿大的友人，曾懸紅三十萬加元緝兇，為加拿大當時同類案件的最大筆懸紅賞金。 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=891602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D891602&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=795e2f50\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=891602</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n本港入境處處長梁銘彥的女兒，在就讀的大學被人用十字弩射殺，<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>案件至今仍未偵破</strong></span>。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/%E6%A2%81%E9%8A%98%E5%BD%A5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh%2F%25E6%25A2%2581%25E9%258A%2598%25E5%25BD%25A5&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96J8sFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=dfb7b042\" target=\"_blank\">http://zh.wikipedia.org/zh/%E6%A2%81%E9%8A%98%E5%BD%A5</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n梁銘彥與中方過從甚密，在未經批准下與中方官員見面，有可能將英方資料向中方洩露。梁銘彥退休當日，即在下午前往酒店與中方港澳辦官員陳佐洱會面，引人懷疑他向中方投誠。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n梁銘彥隱瞞多項與職位有利益衝突的個人投資活動，包括隱瞞在中國大陸的投資、未有申報在三間私人公司擁有股權，而其中兩間公司，即「新中港廣告公司」及「Dragon House Investments」更與中國大陸有一定聯繫。除此之外，梁銘彥逾期償還公務員置業貸款，透過公務員置業貸款在加拿大購買市值過百萬元的物業以轉售圖利。"},{"pid":"939f332cea80544d8918a700e6defad8b4ff967c","tid":1206041,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:20:48.000Z","msg":"推，等有無其他消息"},{"pid":"df94cb78efb5e614c159853298227bf37718d1e8","tid":1206041,"uid":164690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:21:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f32b946ef33d3492c668c8dbfeffe2b401a0db0","tid":1206041,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df94cb78efb5e614c159853298227bf37718d1e8","tid":1206041,"uid":164690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:21:56.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:34:16.000Z","msg":"梁銘彦，仲以為係梁君彦添"},{"pid":"734a2e5bda1760b739d19900aead7dc4566d9f5c","tid":1206041,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"939f332cea80544d8918a700e6defad8b4ff967c","tid":1206041,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T01:20:48.000Z","msg":"推，等有無其他消息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:37:22.000Z","msg":"屌，2004新聞黎，15年前"}]}